items.title: Race for 2nd AL Wild Card spot heating up
items.summary: The Twins and Angels have shadowed one another for the past 35 days, each taking turns ahead of the other, neither opening up more than a two-game advantage. Isn't that the definition of a great playoff chase? At the moment, there's your race for the second American League Wild Card berth.
